cc:Work.dc:title: Each clipart has simple share widgets
cc:Work.dc:description: You can see quick SVG, PNG, and PDF linking in action directly here: http://openclipart.org/detail/188332/chateau-bucovice-by-jarda-188332 Now, these three options are included on each clipart page. Openclipart encourages everyone to freely use and share clipart from Openclipart all over the web, in presentations, your apps, books and more! Have fun and be creative!
